<title>Upload photos to <app>PicasaWeb</app></title>

<p><em>PicasaWeb</em> is a photo album service that lets you share pictures with
people online. You can add a shortcut button that provides a convenient way of uploading 
pictures to PicasaWeb.</p>

<p>To do this, make sure that <link xref="plugins">eog-plugins</link> is
installed. Then, click <guiseq><gui>Edit</gui><gui>Preferences</gui></guiseq>,
go to the <gui>Plugins</gui> tab and check <gui>PicasaWeb Uploader</gui>.</p>
<p>This will give you a convenient <guiseq><gui>Tools</gui><gui>Upload to
PicasaWeb</gui></guiseq> menu item.</p>

